With zip closure and pocket on front, easy-open pullers and side mesh pockets. Padded and adjustable back and shoulder straps. RPET emblem on label and available in a wide range of colours.

data.description: 138x72cm towel in absorbent and soft microfiber of 200g/m2 in varied colors. Presented in a practical mesh bag with adjustable accessory. *For orders with printing, the cost of marking must be increased + 0.20 / unit for special handling.*

data.title: Stalon
data.description: Complete set of elastic bands to stay fit outdoors or at home. Including 5 rubber bands in different colours, each one with a different resistance level:  Yellow band up to 4.5 kg Blue band up to 6.8 kg Green band up to 9.1 kg Black band up to 11.4 kg  Red band up to 13.6 kg  Including metal carabiners for a secure fit, 2 non-slip hand grips, door anchor attachment and 2 ankle belts. Presented in an individual bag with drawstring closure and fitting accessory + design box. With user manual in English and Spanish.

data.description: Nature line game set. Including a deck of french playing cards in recycled cardboard and domino in wood. Set presented inside a wooden case with individual compartments for each game and slide-opening lid.

Padded shoulder straps with adjustable shoulder straps and buckle closure.

Padded interior compartment for laptop up to 15 inches and pocket for tablet up to 11 inches. Padded, adjustable shoulder straps.
